arts.ttl: Netherlands beat Malta 4-0 to open three-point lead in World Cup qualifying group
arts.sum: Netherlands forward Cody Gakpo converted two penalties while Tijjani Reijnders and Memphis Depay also scored in a 4-0 win away to Malta on Thursday as the Dutch opened up a three-point lead in World Cup qualifying Group G.

arts.ttl: Gakpo leads Netherlands to win over Malta
